item.title: You Won't Believe How Far This World Record Paper Airplane Can Fly!
item.description: You Won’t Believe How Far This World Record Paper Airplane Can Fly! We’ve all made paper airplanes as kids, but few of us have achieved the same level of success as John Collins Collins is the creator of the world record-breaking paper airplane, which has been recognized by the Guinness World Records for its impressive flight Introduction John Collins is the creator of the world record-breaking paper airplane. His design is based on the classic paper airplane, but with some modifications to make it more aerodynamic and capable of flying farther.
